description: This file sets up an evaluation for a multi-language team using AI agents, including defining agents, a team, and running an accuracy evaluation.

classes.name: Agent
classes.description: Represents an AI agent with a name, role, and model.

classes.name: Team
classes.description: Represents a team of agents with routing capabilities.

classes.name: AccuracyEval
classes.description: Handles the evaluation of accuracy for a given team and input.

classes.name: AccuracyResult
classes.description: Stores the result of an accuracy evaluation, including average score.

methods.name: run
methods.description: Executes the accuracy evaluation and returns the result.
